quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  17,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  17,1,woh ( zaat ) pak hai jo aik raat apne bande ko msjdalhram yani ( Khana kaaba ) se masjid aqsa ( yani beeet almuqaddas ) taq jis ke gurda gird hum ne barkaten rakhi hain le gaya taakay hum usay apni ( qudrat ki ) nishanain deikhein. be shak woh suneney wala ( aur ) dekhnay wala hai
  17,2,aur hum ne moose ko kitaab inayat ki thi aur is ko bani Israel ke liye rehnuma muqarrarkiya tha ke mere siwa kisi ko karsaaz nah thehrana
  17,3,ae unn logon ki aulaad jin ko hum ne Nooh ke sath ( kashti mein ) sawaarkiya tha. be shak Nooh ( hamaray ) shukar guzar bande they
  17,4,aur hum ne kitaab mein bani Israel se keh diya tha ke zameen mein do dafaa fasaad مچاؤ ge aur barri sar kashi karo ge
  17,5,pas jab pehlay ( waday ) ka waqt aaya to hum ne sakht larai larnay walay bande tum par musallat kardiye aur woh shehron ke andar phail gay. aur woh wada poora ho kar raha
  17,6,phir hum ne doosri baat tum ko unn par ghalba diya aur maal aur beiton se tumhari madad ki. aur tum ko jamaat kaseer bana diya
  17,7,agar tum نneko karikaro ge to apni jaanun ke liye karo ge. aur agar aamaal bad karo ge to ( unn ka ) wabaal bhi tumhari hi jaanun par hoga phir jab dosray ( waday ) ka waqt aaya ( to hum ne phir apne bande beje ) taakay tumahray cheharon ko bigaar den aur jis terhan pehli dafaa masjid ( beeet almuqaddas ) mein daakhil hogaye they isi terhan phir is mein daakhil ho jaien aur jis cheez par ghalba payen ussay tabah kar dein
  17,8,"umeed hai ke tumhara perwar-digaar tum par reham kere, aur agar tum phir wohi ( harkatein ) karo ge to hum bhi ( wohi pehla sulooq ) karen ge aur hum ne jahannum ko kafiroon ke liye qaid khanah bana rakha hai"
  17,9,yeh quran woh rasta dekhata hai jo sab se seedha hai aur mominoun ko jo naik amal karte hain basharat deta hai ke unn ke liye ajar azeem hai
  17,10,aur yeh bhi ( batata hai ) ke jo akhirat par imaan nahi rakhtay unn ke liye hum ne dukh dainay wala azaab tayyar kar rakha hai
  17,11,aur ensaan jis terhan ( jaldi se ) bhalai mangta hai isi terhan buraiee mangta hai. aur ensaan jald baz ( peda howa ) hai
  17,12,aur hum ne din aur raat ko do nishanain banaya hai raat ki nishani ko tareek banaya aur din ki nishani ko roshan. taakay tum apne perwar-digaar ka fazl ( yani ) rozi talaash karo aur barson ka shumaar aur hisaab jano. aur hum ne har cheez ko ( bakhoobi ) tafseel kar di hai
  17,13,aur hum ne har ensaan ke aamaal ko ( bah soorat kitaab ) is ke gilaay mein latka diya hai. aur qayamat ke roz ( woh ) kitaab usay nikaal deikhein ge jisay woh khula howa dekhe ga
  17,14,( kaha jaye ga ke ) apni kitaab parh le. to aaj apna aap hi Muhasib kaafi hai
  17,15,jo shakhs hadaayat ikhtiyar karta hai to apne liye ikhtiyar karta hai. aur jo gumraah hota hai gumraahi ka zarrar bhi isi ko hoga. aur koi shakhs kisi dosray ka boojh nahi uthaye ga. aur jab taq hum paighambar nah bhaij len azaab nahi diya karte
  17,16,aur jab hamara iradah kisi bastii ke halaak karne ka howa to wahan ke aasooda logon ko ( fwahish par ) mamoor kardiya to woh nafarmaniyan karte rahay. phir is par ( azaab ka ) hukum saabit hogaya. aur hum ne usay halaak kar dala
  17,17,aur hum ne Nooh ke baad bohat si amtoN ko halaak kar dala. aur tumhara perwar-digaar apne bundon ke gunaaho ko jan-nay aur dekhnay wala kaafi hai
  17,18,jo shakhs duniya ( ki aasoudgi ) ka khawahish mand ho to hum is mein se jisay chahtay hain aur jitna chahtay hain jald day dete hain. phir is ke liye jahannum ko ( thikana ) muqarrar kar rakha hai. jis mein woh nafreen sun kar aur ( dargaah khuda se ) raandah ho kar daakhil hoga
  17,19,aur jo shakhs akhirat ka khawastgah howa aur is mein itni koshish kere jitni usay Laiq hai aur woh momin bhi ho to aisay hi logon ki koshish thikaane lagti hai
  17,20,hum unn ko aur un ko sab ko tumahray perwar-digaar ki bakhshish se madad dete hain. aur tumahray perwar-digaar ki bakhshish ( kisi se ) ruki hui nahi
  17,21,dekho hum ne kis terhan baaz ko baaz par fazeelat bakhsh hai. aur akhirat darjon mein ( duniya se ) bohat bartar aur bartari mein kahin barh kar hai
  17,22,aur khuda ke sath koi aur mabood nah banana ke mlammatain sun kar aur baykas ho kar baithy reh jao ge
  17,23,aur tumahray perwar-digaar ne irshad farmaya hai ke is ke siwa kisi ki ibadat nah karo aur maa baap ke sath bhalai karte raho. agar un mein se aik ya dono tumahray samnay burhapay ko poanch jayen to unn ko uff taq nah kehna aur nah inhen jhidakna aur unn se baat adab ke sath karna
  17,24,aur ijzo niaz se un ke agay jhuke raho aur un ke haq mein dua karo ke ae perwar-digaar jaissa unhon ne mujhe bachpan mein ( shafqat se ) parwarishkiya hai to bhi unn ( ke haal ) par rehmat farma
  17,25,jo kuch tumahray dilon mein hai tumhara perwar-digaar is se bakhoobi waaqif hai. agar tum naik hogay to woh rujoo laane walon ko bakhash dainay wala hai
  17,26,aur rishta daaron aur mohtajon aur musafiron ko un ka haq ada karo. aur fuzool kharchi se maal nah urrao
  17,27,ke fuzool kharchi karne walay to shetan ke bhai hain. aur shetan apne perwar-digaar ( ki nematon ) ka kufar un karne wala ( yani nashukara ) hai
  17,28,aur agar tum ne apne perwar-digaar ki rehmat ( yani farakh dasti ) ke intzaar mein jis ki tumhe umeed ho un ( msthqin ) ki taraf tavajja nah krsko unn se narmi se baat keh diya karo
  17,29,aur apne haath ko nah to gardan se bandha howa ( yani bohat tang ) karlo ( ke kisi kuch do hi nahi ) aur nah bilkul khol hi do ( ke sabhi day daalo aur injaam yeh ho ) ke malamat zada aur darmandah ho kar baith jao
  17,30,be shak tumhara perwar-digaar jis ki rozi chahta hai farakh kardaita hai aur ( jis ki rozi chahta hai ) tang kardaita hai woh apne bundon se khabardaar hai aur ( un ko ) dekh raha hai
  17,31,aur apni aulaad ko muflisi ke khauf se qatal nah karna. ( kyunkay ) un ko aur tum ko hum hi rizaq dete hain. kuch shak nahi ke un ka maar daalna bara sakht gunah hai
  17,32,aur zina ke bhi paas nah jana ke woh be hiyai aur buri raah hai
  17,33,aur jis ka jandaar ka maarna khuda ne haraamkiya hai usay qatal nah karna magar jaaiz tor par ( yani ba fatwa Shariat ). aur jo shakhs zulm se qatalkiya jaye hum ne is ke waris ko ikhtiyar diya hai ( ke zalim qaatil se badla le ) to is ko chahiye ke qatal ( ke qisaas ) mein zayad-ti nah kere ke woh mansoor o fatahyaab hai
  17,34,aur yateem ke maal ke paas bhi nah phatakna magar aisay tareeq se ke bohat behtar ho yahan taq ke ho jawani ko poanch jaye. aur ehad ko poora karo ke ehad ke baray mein zaroor prssh hogi
  17,35,aur jab ( koi cheez ) naap kar dainay lagu to pemana poora bhara karo aur ( jab toal kar do to ) traazo seedhi rakh kar tola karo. yeh bohat achi baat aur injaam ke lehaaz se bhi bohat behtar hai
  17,36,aur ( ae bande ) jis cheez ka tujhe ilm nahi is ke peechay nah par. ke kaan aur aankhh aur dil un sab ( jwarah) se zaroor baz pursi hogi
  17,37,aur zameen par akarr kar ( aur tan kar ) mat chal ke to zameen ko phaar to nahi daaley ga aur nah lamba ho kar pahoron ( ki chouti ) taq poanch jaye ga
  17,38,un sab ( aadato ) ki buraiee tairay perwar-digaar ke nazdeek bohat napasand hai
  17,39,ae paighambar yeh un ( hdayton ) mein se hain jo khuda ne danai ki baatein tumhari taraf wahi ki hain. aur khuda ke sath koi mabood nah banana ke ( aisa karne se ) malamat zada aur ( dargaah khuda se ) raandah bana kar jahannum mein daal diye jao ge
  17,40,( mushrako! )kiya tumahray perwar-digaar ne tum ko larke diye aur khud firshton ko betiyan banaya. kuch shak nahi ke ( yeh ) tum barri ( namaqool baat ) kehte ho
  17,41,aur hum ne is quran mein terhan terhan ki baatein bayan ki hain taakay log nasiyaat pakren ge. magar woh is se aur bdk jatay hain
  17,42,keh do ke agar khuda ke sath aur mabood hotay jaissa ke yeh kehte hain to woh zaroor ( khuday-e ) maalik arsh ki taraf ( larnay bhernay ke liye ) rasta nikaltay
  17,43,woh pak hai aur jo kuch yeh bakwaas karte hain is se ( is ka rutba ) bohat aliiiii hai
  17,44,saton aasman aur zameen aur jo log un mein hain sab isi ki tasbeeh karte hain. aur ( makhloqaat mein se ) koi cheez nahi magar is ki tareef ke sath tasbeeh karti hai. lekin tum un ki tasbeeh ko nahi samajte. be shak woh Burdbar ( aur ) Ghafar hai
  17,45,aur jab quran parha karte ho to hum tum mein aur un logon mein jo akhirat par imaan nahi rakhtay hijaab par hijaab kar dete hain
  17,46,aur un ke dilon par parda daal dete hain ke usay samajh nah saken aur un ke kaanon mein saqal peda kar dete hain. aur jab tum quran mein apne perwar-digaar yaktaa ka zikar karte ho to woh bdk jatay aur peeth phair kar chal dete hain
  17,47,yeh log jab tumhari taraf kaan lagatay hain to jis niyat se yeh suntay hain hum usay khoob jantay hain aur jab yeh sargoshian karte hain ( yani ) jab zalim kehte hain ke tum aik aisay shakhs ki pairwi karte ho jis par jaadookiya gaya hai
  17,48,dekho unhon ne kis kis terhan ki tumahray baray mein baatein banayen hain. so yeh gumraah ho rahay hain aur rasta nahi paskte
  17,49,aur kehte hain ke jab hum ( mar kar boseedah ) hadion aur chuur chuur ho jaien ge tokiya az sar e no peda ho kar uthen ge
  17,50,keh do ke ( khuwa tum ) pathar hojao ya loha
  17,51,ya koi aur cheez jo tumahray nazdeek ( pathar aur lohay se bhi ) barri ( sakht ) ho ( jhat kahin ge ) ke ( bhala ) hamein dobarah kon Jalaaye ga? keh do ke wohi jis ne tum ko pehli baar pedakiya. to ( taajjub se ) tumahray agay sar hila-ayn ge aur poucheen ge ke aisa kab hoga? keh do ke umeed hai jald hoga
  17,52,jis din woh tumhe pukare ga to tum is ki tareef ke sath jawab do ge aur khayaal karo ge ke tum ( duniya mein ) bohat kam ( muddat ) rahay
  17,53,aur mere bundon se keh do ke ( logon se ) aisi baatein kaha karen jo bohat pasandeeda hon. kyunkay shetan ( buri baton se ) un mein fasaad dalwa deta hai. kuch shak nahi ke shetan ensaan ka khula dushman hai
  17,54,tumhara perwar-digaar tum se khoob waaqif hai. agar chahay to tum par reham kere ya agar chahay to tumhe azaab day. aur hum ne tum ko un par Darogha ( bana kar ) nahi bheja
  17,55,aur jo log asmano aur zameen mein hain tumhara perwar-digaar un se khoob waaqif hai. aur hum ne baaz payghambaroon ko baaz par fazeelat bakhsh aur dawod ko Zaboor inayat ki
  17,56,kaho ke ( mushrako ) jin logon ki nisbat tumhe ( mabood honay ka ) gumaan hai un ko bulaa kar dekho. woh tum se takleef ke daur karne ya is ke badal dainay ka kuch bhi ikhtiyar nahi rakhtay
  17,57,yeh log jin ko ( khuda ke siwa ) pkarte hain woh khud apne perwar-digaar ke haan zareya ( taqarab ) talaash karte rehtay hain ke kon un mein ( khuda ka ) ziyada Maqarrab hota hai aur is ki rehmat ke umeed waar rehtay hain aur is ke azaab se khauf rakhtay hain. be shak tumahray perwar-digaar ka azaab darny ki cheez hai
  17,58,aur ( kufar karne walon ki ) koi bastii nahi magar qayamat ke din se pehlay hum usay halaak kar dein ge ya sakht azaab se moazzib karen ge. yeh kitaab ( yani taqdeer ) mein likha ja chuka hai
  17,59,aur hum ne nishanain bhijni is liye moqoof kar dein ke aglay logon ne is ki takzieeb ki thi. aur hum ne smod ko oontni ( nabuwat Saleh ki khuli ) nishani di. to unhon ne is par zulmkiya aur hum jo nishanain bheja karte hain to darane ko
  17,60,jab hum ne tum se kaha ke tumhara perwar-digaar logon ko ihata kiye hue hai. aur jo numaish hum ne tumhe dikhayi is ko logon ke liye aazmaish kiya. aur isi terhan ( thohar ke ) darakht ko jis par quran mein laanat ki gayi. aur hum inhen darate hain to un ko is se barri ( sakht ) sar kashi peda hoti hai
  17,61,aur jab hum ne firshton se kaha ke aadam ko sajda karo to sab ne sajdakiya magar iblees ne nahkiya. bola ke bhala mein aisay shakhs ko sajda karo jis ko to ne matti se pedakiya hai
  17,62,( aur az raah tanz ) kehnay laga ke dekh to yahi woh hai jisay to ne mujh par fazeelat di hai. agar to mujh ko qayamat ke din taq mohlat day to mein thoray se shakhson ke siwa is ki ( tamam ) aulaad ki jarr kaatta rahon ga
  17,63,khuda ne farmaya ( yahan se ) chala ja. jo shakhs un mein se teri pairwi kere ga to tum sab ki jaza jahannum hai ( aur woh ) poori saza ( hai )
  17,64,aur un mein se jis ko b_hka sakay apni aawaz se behkata reh. aur un par apne sawaron aur pyaron ko charha kar lata reh aur un ke maal aur aulaad mein shareek hota reh aur un se waday karta reh. aur shetan jo waday un se karta hai sab dhoka hai
  17,65,jo mere ( mukhlis ) bande hain un par tera kuch zor nahi. aur ( ae paighambar ) tumhara perwar-digaar karsaaz kaafi hai
  17,66,tumhara perwar-digaar woh hai jo tumahray liye darya mein kashtiyan chalata hai taakay tum is ke fazl se ( rozi ) talaash karo. be shak woh tum par meharban hai
  17,67,aur jab tum ko darya mein takleef pahunchti hai ( yani doobnay ka khauf hota hai ) to jin ko tum puraka karte ho sab is ( perwar-digaar ) ke siwa gum ho jatay hain. phir jab woh tum ko ( doobnay se ) bacha kar khushki par le jata hai to tum munh phair letay ho aur ensaan hai hi nashukara
  17,68,kiya tum ( is se ) be khauf ho ke khuda tumhe khushki ki taraf ( le ja kar zameen mein ) dhansa day ya tum par sangrayzon ki bhari hui aandhi chala de. phir tum apna koi nigehbaan nah pao
  17,69,ya ( is se ) be khauf ho kar tum doosri dafaa darya mein le jaye phir tum par taiz howa chalaye aur tumahray kufar ke sabab tumhe duubo day. phir tum is ghark ke sabab apne liye koi hamara peecha karne wala nah pao
  17,70,aur hum ne bani aadam ko izzat bakhsh aur un ko jungle aur darya mein sawari di aur pakeeza rozi ataa ki aur apni bohat si makhloqaat par fazeelat di
  17,71,jis din hum sab logon ko un ke pishwaon ke sath bulayen ge. to jin ( ke aamaal ) ki kitaab un ke dahinay haath mein di jaye gi woh apni kitaab ko ( khush ho ho kar ) parheen ge aur un par dhaagay barabar bhi zulm nah hoga
  17,72,aur jo shakhs is ( duniya ) mein andha ho woh akhirat mein bhi andha hoga. aur ( nijaat ke ) raste se bohat daur
  17,73,aur ae paighambar jo wahi hum ne tumhari taraf bhaije hai qareeb tha ke yeh ( kafir ) log tum ko is se bchla den taakay tum is ke siwa aur baatein hamari nisbat banalo. aur is waqt woh tum ko dost bana letay
  17,74,aur agar tum ko saabit qadam nah rehne dete to tum kisi qader un ki taraf mael honay hi lagey they
  17,75,is waqt hum tum ko zindagi mein ( azaab ka ) dona aur marnay par bhi dona maza chukhate phir tum hamaray muqablay mein kisi ko apna madadgaar nah paate
  17,76,aur qareeb tha ke yeh log tumhe zameen ( mecca ) se phsla den taakay tumhe wahan se jalaa-watan kar den. aur is waqt tumahray peechay yeh bhi nah rehtay magar kam
  17,77,jo paighambar hum ne tum se pehlay beje they un ka ( aur un ke baray mein hamara yahi ) tareeq raha hai aur tum hamaray tareeq mein taghay o tabaddul nah pao ge
  17,78,"( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) Sooraj ke dhalnay se raat ke andheray taq ( Zahar , asar, maghrib, asha ki ) namazain aur subah ko quran parha karo. kyun subah ke waqt quran ka parhna mojab huzoor ( mulaika ) hai"
  17,79,aur baaz hissa shab mein beedar howa karo ( aur t_hjd ki namaz parha karo ). ( yeh shab khaizi ) tumhari liye ( sabab ) Zayadat hai ( sawab aur namaz t_hjd tum ko Nafil ) hai qareeb hai ke khuda tum ko maqam Mahmood mein daakhil kere
  17,80,aur kaho ke ae perwar-digaar mujhe ( madeeney mein ) achi terhan daakhil kejio aur ( mukkay se ) achi terhan نکالیو. aur apne haan se zor o quwat ko mera madadgaar banaiyo
  17,81,aur keh do ke haq agaya aur baatil nabood hogaya. be shak baatil nabood honay wala hai
  17,82,aur hum quran ( ke zariye ) se woh cheez nazil karte hain jo mominoun ke liye Shifa aur rehmat hai aur zaalmon ke haq mein to is se nuqsaan hi barhta hai
  17,83,aur jab hum ensaan ko Nemat bkhshte hain to rugardan ho jata aur pehlu phair laita hai. aur jab usay sakhti pahunchti hai to na umeed hojata hai
  17,84,keh do ke har shakhs apne tareeq ke mutabiq amal karta hai. so tumhara perwar-digaar is shakhs se khoob waaqif hai jo sab se ziyada seedhay raste par hai
  17,85,aur tum se rooh ke baray mein sawal karte hain. keh do ke woh mere perwar-digaar ki aik shaan hai aur tum logon ko ( bohat hi ) kam ilm diya gaya hai
  17,86,aur agar hum chahain to jo ( kitaab ) hum tumhari taraf bhaijtay hain usay ( dilon se ) mehv kar dein. phir tum is ke liye hamaray muqablay mein kisi ko madadgaar nah pao
  17,87,magar ( is ka qaim rehna ) tumahray perwar-digaar ki rehmat hai. kuch shak nahi ke tum par is ka bara fazl hai
  17,88,keh do ke agar ensaan aur jin is baat par mujtma hon ke is quran jaissa bana layein to is jaissa nah laskin ge agarchay woh aik dosray ko madadgaar hon
  17,89,aur hum ne quran mein sab baatein terhan terhan se bayan kar di hain. magar aksar logon ne inkaar karne ke siwa qubool nahkiya
  17,90,aur kehnay lagey ke hum tum par imaan nahi layein ge jab taq ke ( ajeeb vghrib baatein nah dikhao yani ya to ) hamaray liye zameen se chashma jari kardo
  17,91,ya tumhara khajoron aur angarro ka koi baagh ho aur is ke beech mein nehrain baha nikalu
  17,92,ya jaissa tum kaha karte ho hum par aasman ke tukre laa girao ya khuda aur firshton ko ( hamaray ) samnay lao
  17,93,ya to tumhara sonay ka ghar ho ya tum aasman par charh jao. aur hum tumahray charhne ko bhi nahi manen ge jab taq ke koi kitaab nah lao jisay hum parh bhi len. keh do ke mera perwar-digaar pak hai mein to sirf aik pegham pohanchanay wala ensaan hon
  17,94,aur jab logon ke paas hadaayat aagai to un ko imaan laane se is ke siwa koi cheez Maney nah hui ke kehnay lagey kekiya khuda ne aadmi ko paighambar karkay bheja hai
  17,95,keh do ke agar zameen mein farishtay hotay ( ke is mein ) chaltay phirtay ( aur ) aaraam karte ( yani baste ) to hum unn ke paas farishtay ko paighambar bana kar bhaijtay
  17,96,keh do ke mere aur tumahray darmain khuda hi gawah kaafi hai. wohi apne bundon se khabardaar ( aur un ko ) dekhnay wala hai
  17,97,aur jis shakhs ko khuda hadaayat day wohi hadaayat yab hai. aur jin ko gumraah kere to tum khuda ke siwa unn ke Rafeeq nahi pao ge. aur hum unn ko qayamat ke din avndhe munh andhay gungay aur behray ( bana kar ) utthayen ge. aur un ka thikana dozakh hai. jab ( is ki aag ) bujhnay ko hogi to hum un ko ( azaab dainay ke liye ) aur bahrakna den ge
  17,98,yeh un ki saza hai is liye ke woh hamari aayton se kufar karte they aur kehte they ke jab hum ( mar kar boseedah ) haddiyan aur rezah rezah ho jaien ge tokiya az sar e no peda kiye jayen ge
  17,99,kiya unhon ne nahi dekha ke khuda jis ne asmano aur zameen ko pedakiya hai is baat par Qadir hai ke un jaisay ( log ) peda kardey. aur is ne un ke liye aik waqt muqarrar kar diya hai jis mein kuch bhi shak nahi. to zaalmon ne inkaar karne ke siwa ( usay ) qubool nahkiya
  17,100,keh do ke agar mere perwar-digaar ki rehmat ke khazanay tumahray haath mein hotay to tum kharch hojane ke khauf se ( un ko ) band rakhtay. aur ensaan dil ka bohat tang hai
  17,101,aur hum ne moose ko no khuli nishanain den to bani Israel se daryaft karlo ke jab woh un ke paas aeye to firaon ne un se kaha ke moose mein khayaal karta hon ke tum par jaadookiya gaya hai
  17,102,unhon ne kaha ke tum yeh jantay ho ke asmano aur zameen ke perwar-digaar ke siwa un ko kisi ne nazil nahikiya. ( aur woh bhi tum logon ke ) samjhane ko. aur ae firaon mein khayaal karta hon ke tum halaak hojao ge
  17,103,to is ne chaha ke un ko sir zameen ( misar ) se nikaal day to hum ne is ko aur jo is ke sath they sab ko duubo diya
  17,104,aur is ke baad bani Israel se kaha ke tum is malik mein raho saho. phir jab akhirat ka wada aajay ga to hum tum sab ko jama karkay le ayen ge
  17,105,aur hum ne is quran ko sachaai ke sath nazilkiya hai aur woh sachaai ke sath nazil howa aur ( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) hum ne tum ko sirf khushkhabri dainay wala aur dar sunanay wala bana kar bheja hai
  17,106,aur hum ne quran ko juzo juazo karkay nazilkiya hai taakay tum logon ko tehr tehr kar parh kar sunaaoo aur hum ne is ko aahista aahista utaara hai
  17,107,keh do ke tum is par imaan lao ya nah lao ( yeh fi nafsa haq hai ) jin logon ko is se pehlay ilm ( kitaab ) diya hai. jab woh un ko parh kar sunaya jata hai to woh thoriyon ke bil sjday mein gir parte hain
  17,108,aur kehte hain ke hamara perwar-digaar pak hai be shak hamaray perwar-digaar ka wada poora ho kar raha
  17,109,aur woh thoriyon ke bil gir parte hain ( aur ) rotay jatay hain aur is se un ko aur ziyada aajzi peda hoti hai
  17,110,keh do ke tum ( khuda ko ) allah ( ke naam se ) poukaro ya rehman ( ke naam se ) jis naam se poukaro is ke sab achay naam hain. aur namaz nah buland aawaz se parho aur nah aahista balkay is ke beech ka tareeqa ikhtiyar karo
  17,111,aur kaho ke sab tareef khuda hi ko hai jis ne nah to kisi ko beta banaya hai aur nah is ki badshahi mein koi shareek hai aur nah is wajah se ke woh aajiz o natawan hai koi is ka madadgaar hai aur is ko bara jaan kar is ki barayi karte raho
